      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS fazzija\nas Mohsu: Issteep tawu Rohku\npahr to Juhru/ ka tas Uhdens\nfagahschahs pahr teem Egipte-\nteem/ pahr winnu Ratteem/ un\npahr winnu Jahtneekenu."
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad issteepu Mohsus fa-\nott Rohku pahr to Juhru/ un ta\nuhra atgreeſahs paſchâ Rihta-\nrehflâ fawâ Straunê/ un tee\ngipteri behdse winnam pretti/\ntas KUNGS eegahſe tohs\ngipterus Juhrus * widdû.\n* Ittin kâ tee to Israëlitezu Behrnias ap-\nzinaja, z. Mohs: Gr: 1,22. tà patt teem\nak noteek."
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo kad tas Uhdens atgree-\nhs/ tad apkahje tas tohs Rat-\ns un Jahtneekus/ wiſfu Wa-\nnis Spehku/tas winnam Juh-\nbija pakak gahjis/ ka ne weens\nteem atlifke."
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet Israëta Behrni gah-\ntaufahm Kabjahm Juhras\niddû/ un tas Uhdens bija teem\nr Muhri pa labbo un kreifo\nohku."
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta isgtabbe tas KUNGS\nmi Deena Israëln no to E-\ntern Rohkas/ un Israëls re-\nja tohs Egipterus nomirru-\nus Juhras Mallâ."
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Israëts redjeja arridsan to\nu Rohku/ ko tas KUNGS\nteem Egiptereem bij parah-\ns. Un tee Landis bibjajahs to\nNGU/ un tizzeja tam KUN-\nAM un winna Kalpan Moh-\nm."
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "KUNGAM teizamu Dseesmu: i. Mirjam\nun wiſas Geewas pateiz tam KUNGAM\nar Bungahm un Stabbulehw: 20. Israëls\nfurne prett Mohsu ta ruhka Mahras Uh-\ndens dehi: 22/ 24. Kas zaar Brihnumu-\nfalds tohp: 25. Isseet prohjam/ un apmet-\ntahs eeksh Eelim: 27."
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ad dseedaja Mohsus un\nIsraëta Behrni tam\nKUNGAM fcho Dsees-\nmu/ un fazzija: Es dseedafchu\ntam KUNGAM/ jo wiſch iru\ntohti pa-augstinajees: Sirgus\nun winno Jahtneekus irr wiſch\nJuhra eegahsis."
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS irr mans\nSpehks/ un manna Dseesina/ un\nwiſch irr man par Pestischanu\nbijis: Schis irr mans STIP-\nRAJS DEEWS/ es pagoh-\ndinaschu winnu: Wiſch irr\nmanna Tehwa Deews/ es pa-\naugstinachu winnu."
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS irr tas\nRatta-Wihrs / KUNGS irr\nwinna Wahrdg."
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiſch irr Warais Rat-\ntus/ un winna Spehku Juhra-\neemettis/ un tee winna islaſſiti\nWirfneeki irr apflihkutchi Needru-\nJuhra."
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tee Dſittumi irr tohs ap-\nklaſſuchi / tee irr Dibbina no-\ngrimmufchi ka Akmins."
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ak KUNGS! tawa labba\nRohka irr pagohdinata zaar\nSpehku/ tawa labba Rohka/ al\nKUNGS! irr tohs Gennaidneekue-\nfalausijji."
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un zaar tawu leelu Aug-\nstutnu eſſi tu tawus Prettinee-"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
